"适用场景\n• 你想让模型在聊天时执行特定任务，例如格式化输出、代码检查、知识问答等。\n• 你希望将常用的提示词或操作封装为可复用的技能模块。\n\n怎么用（建议顺序）\n1. 点击\"新增技能\"粘贴 SKILL.md，或通过 GitHub / 本地文件导入。\n2. 确认技能列表中对应技能已启用（右侧开关为开）。\n3. 打开\"向模型暴露 Agent Skills（use_skill）\"总开关。\n4. 在聊天中告知模型你的需求，模型会在合适时机调用 use_skill。\n\nSKILL.md 格式说明\n• 文件头（frontmatter）可声明 name、description、when_to_use 等字段。\n• 导入目录或仓库时，省略 name 会使用技能目录名；省略 description 会使用正文首段。\n• name 作为技能的唯一标识，不能与已有技能重名。\n• 正文可包含使用说明、参数说明、示例等任意 Markdown 内容。\n\n常见问题\n• 模型不调用技能：先检查总开关是否已开启，并确认对应技能已启用。\n• 导入失败：检查仓库地址是否可访问，或改用本地文件/手动粘贴 SKILL.md 内容。\n• 技能内容需更新：进入技能详情编辑 SKILL.md 文件即可。" = "When to use this\n• You want the model to perform specific tasks in chat, such as formatting output, code review, or knowledge Q&A.\n• You want to package common prompts or operations into reusable skill modules.\n\nHow to use (recommended order)\n1. Tap Add Skill to paste SKILL.md, or import from GitHub / local files.\n2. Confirm the skill is enabled in the skill list.\n3. Turn on the master switch that exposes Agent Skills (use_skill) to the model.\n4. Tell the model what you need in chat; it will call use_skill when appropriate.\n\nSKILL.md format\n• The frontmatter can declare name, description, when_to_use, and other fields.\n• When importing a directory or repository, an omitted name uses the skill directory name; an omitted description uses the first body paragraph.\n• name is the unique skill identifier and cannot duplicate an existing skill.\n• The body may contain usage instructions, parameter notes, examples, or any Markdown content.\n\nCommon issues\n• Model does not call a skill: check that the master switch and the individual skill are enabled.\n• Import failed: check repository access, or use local file / manual SKILL.md paste.\n• Need updates: edit SKILL.md from the skill detail page.";
